<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-11026] OOM due to HeapByteBuffer instances</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-11026</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Cassandra 3.0.2 fails with OOM. The heapdump shows large number of HeapByteBuffer instances, each retaining 1Mb (see the details on the screenshot). Overall retained size is ~2Gb.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We can provide the additional info and the whole heapdump if necessary.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
